properties.Name: RequisitionLineItem
properties.Description: The specific Item(s) detailed for the associated Requisition.

Columns.Name: RequisitionId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Requisition.

Columns.Name: RequisitionLineItemNumber
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the Requisition Line Item.

Columns.Name: DiscountPerItemUnitAmount
Columns.Description: The per unit Item discount provided by the Vendor.

Columns.Name: RequisitionPerUnitItemPrice
Columns.Description: The Item per unit price applied to the Requisition.

Columns.Name: QualityStandardMeasure
Columns.Description:
The specific Quality Standard metric assigned to the RFI/RFP/PO etc.

Example:

Quality Standard = PPM (Parts Per Million defective)
Quality Standard Measure = 100 (100 parts may be defective per million parts)

Columns.Name: QualityStandardId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the Quality Standard.

Columns.Name: ItemSku
Columns.Description: The Stock Keeping Unit identifier, which is typically used for inventory-related activities.
